---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { translations } from "../i18n/translations";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy â€” Edgar Valdez">
  <Header />
  <main class="legal">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        This privacy policy explains how Edgar Valdez ("I", "me", "my")
        handles information in connection with the website valdezdev.work and
        associated projects.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Information Collection</h2>
      <p>
        This website is a static portfolio site. I do not directly collect,
        store, or process personal data through this website. There are no
        user accounts, forms, cookies, or tracking scripts on this site.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>This website is hosted on Cloudflare Pages, which may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Basic web analytics (page views, country-level location data)
        </li>
        <li>Standard server logs (IP addresses, browser type, timestamps)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        For more information, see
        <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a
        >.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Social Media & API Integrations</h2>
      <p>
        Projects associated with this portfolio may integrate with third-party
        APIs and social media platforms. When using such projects:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Data is processed according to the respective platform's privacy
          policy
        </li>
        <li>
          No social media data is stored on this website or its servers
        </li>
        <li>
          API integrations use only the minimum permissions necessary for
          functionality
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        I do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer any personal information
        to third parties. Any data processed through project integrations
        remains subject to the respective platform's data handling practices.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        This website uses HTTPS encryption via Cloudflare SSL/TLS. While I
        strive to protect any information transmitted to this site, no method
        of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This website is not directed at children under the age of 13. I do
        not knowingly collect any information from children.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        Since this website does not collect personal data, there is generally
        no personal data to access, modify, or delete. If you have concerns
        about data processed through any of my projects, please contact me.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. Changes will be
        reflected on this page with an updated revision date.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For privacy-related questions or concerns, please contact:
        <a href="mailto:contact@valdezdev.work">contact@valdezdev.work</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<script is:inline define:vars={{ translations }}>
  window.__translations = translations;
  if (window.__applyLang && window.__currentLang) {
    window.__applyLang(window.__currentLang);
  }
</script>
